{"tid":123624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲打有無試過比時間自己 最後真係一齊到？","createTime":"2017-02-17T03:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T10:25:12.000Z","uid":50096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d07e35607fc8e8e47f2e65aeafbd71a392ff188","tid":123624,"uid":50096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"我喺一對情侶冷戰期出現左<br />\n好快 佢地分左手 我同左佢一齊<br />\n中間成日對我忽冷忽熱 <br />\n但一齊既時候睇得出佢發自內心咁開心<br />\n可能因為佢Ex太過緊 而我就比到自由<br />\n所以算係一種解放？定搵到個夾既人？<br />\n呢幾日佢都無覆我 一係就隔半日先覆<br />\n我都知佢諗緊好多野 所以都無煩佢<br />\n而尋日終於Send左一大段野比我<br />\n內容主要係 <br />\n佢之前講過話要時間 但無左回事<br />\n然後話好似太快 同埋愈黎愈搵唔到自己<br />\n最後話呢排想自己一個 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以 或者我地可以做友達以上</span><br />\n<br />\n你地教我點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34e9dee051b9419e78ab6490639ea390f085adc","tid":123624,"uid":50096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"啱先開錯台 立即沉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d1e062e644f255646ed6f76084a67793c73059","tid":123624,"uid":50096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"睇黎唔關開錯台事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eca0c7e91d502c4a64caf2b7cebd1a60b72bcfd","tid":123624,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">你咪俾時間佢囉。</span>"},{"pid":"3044b89348aebdd43258c5234f95361eff9656e5","tid":123624,"uid":68712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"佢可能對前度仲有些少掛念，唔能夠全心全意只愛你一個，但又鍾意你對佢好。與其話俾時間自己，不如積極d，時間俾俾下就會錯過左份熱情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7397d924000855750474623acb1a366e18564c14","tid":123624,"uid":52194,"like":0,"disli